To install Python 3.6 and pip (Windows)

Download the Python 3.6 Windows x86-64 executable installer from the downloads page of Python.org.

Run the installer.

Choose Add Python 3.6 to PATH.

Choose Install Now.

-------------------------
Next

To install the AWS CLI with pip (Windows)

>Open the Windows Command Processor from the Start menu.

>Verify that Python and pip are both installed correctly by using the following commands.

>Install the EB CLI using pip/easy_install.

//**Enable to aws eb plugin to push the application.
//**If this plugin is not installed, you cannot push the application and code.
>Issue the below command:C:\Python6> pip install awsebcli --upgrade --user

>After installation check eb using below command :eb --version
